data.description: Caliber Homes open ranch plan with spacious master wing + office/flex on main. This home says welcome home from the moment you step inside the front door. From the tray ceiling to the custom fireplace details and the natural light from all your windows overlooking your backyard. Kitchen features quartz countertops, all appliances, upgraded walk-in pantry and an island. Master suite with double sink vanity, walk-in closet, tile shower and toilet room. We love the vaulted flex/office on the main. Mudroom and Laundry ROOM off of garage make a great drop zone. Lower level is finished with family room, 3 bedrooms and bath. Plenty of storage, 3 car garage, irrigation and generous landscape package.
